{"image_id": "PNR_2014_page_99", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "Pentair plc and Subsidiaries", "bbox": [162.5, 158.9, 405.1, 179.7]}, {"text": "Notes to consolidated financial statements", "bbox": [162.5, 183.9, 524.0, 204.7]}, {"text": "We record penalties and interest related to unrecognized tax benefits in Provision (benefit) for income taxes and", "bbox": [162.5, 233.9, 1112.5, 254.9]}, {"text": "Interest expense, respectively. As of December 31, 2014 and 2013, we have liabilities of $1.2 million and $0.9", "bbox": [162.5, 258.9, 1112.5, 279.9]}, {"text": "million, respectively, for the possible payment of penalties and $9.8 million and $8.9 million, respectively, for", "bbox": [162.5, 284.1, 1112.4, 304.9]}, {"text": "the possible payment of interest expense, which are recorded in Other current liabilities in the Consolidated", "bbox": [162.5, 308.9, 1112.4, 329.9]}, {"text": "Balance Sheets.", "bbox": [162.5, 334.1, 294.5, 354.9]}, {"text": "Deferred taxes in the amount of $11.8 million have been provided on undistributed earnings of certain", "bbox": [162.5, 384.1, 1112.3, 404.9]}, {"text": "subsidiaries. Taxes have not been provided on undistributed earnings of subsidiaries where it is our intention to", "bbox": [162.5, 409.1, 1112.5, 429.9]}, {"text": "reinvest these earnings permanently or to repatriate the earnings only when it is tax effective to do so. It is not", "bbox": [162.5, 434.1, 1112.5, 454.9]}, {"text": "practicable to estimate the amount of tax that might be payable if such earnings were to be remitted.", "bbox": [162.5, 459.1, 997.3, 479.9]}, {"text": "Deferred taxes arise because of different treatment between financial statement accounting and tax accounting,", "bbox": [162.5, 509.1, 1112.4, 529.9]}, {"text": "known as “temporary differences.” We record the tax effect of these temporary differences as “deferred tax", "bbox": [162.5, 534.1, 1112.4, 554.9]}, {"text": "assets” (generally items that can be used as a tax deduction or credit in future periods) and “deferred tax", "bbox": [162.5, 559.1, 1112.4, 579.9]}, {"text": "liabilities” (generally items for which we received a tax deduction but the tax impact has not yet been recorded in", "bbox": [162.5, 584.1, 1112.5, 604.9]}, {"text": "the Consolidated Statements of Operations and Comprehensive Income (Loss)).", "bbox": [162.5, 609.1, 829.4, 629.9]}, {"text": "Deferred taxes were recorded in the Consolidated Balance Sheets as follows:", "bbox": [162.5, 659.1, 804.4, 679.9]}, {"text": "December 31", "bbox": [955.3, 704.7, 1071.7, 725.5]}, {"text": "In millions", "bbox": [162.5, 733.9, 252.2, 754.7]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [938.0, 733.9, 979.7, 754.7]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [1047.4, 733.9, 1089.1, 754.7]}, {"text": "Other current assets", "bbox": [162.5, 767.4, 328.2, 788.2]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [914.6, 767.4, 925.0, 788.2]}, {"text": "139.4", "bbox": [956.3, 767.4, 1003.1, 788.2]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1024.0, 767.4, 1034.4, 788.2]}, {"text": "149.7", "bbox": [1065.6, 767.4, 1112.5, 788.2]}, {"text": "Other non-current assets", "bbox": [162.5, 792.4, 366.4, 813.2]}, {"text": "87.9", "bbox": [966.7, 792.4, 1003.1, 813.2]}, {"text": "92.4", "bbox": [1076.0, 792.4, 1112.5, 813.2]}, {"text": "Deferred tax liabilities", "bbox": [162.5, 817.4, 350.2, 838.2]}, {"text": "528.3", "bbox": [956.3, 817.4, 1003.1, 838.2]}, {"text": "557.0", "bbox": [1065.6, 817.4, 1112.5, 838.2]}, {"text": "Net deferred tax liabilities", "bbox": [162.5, 850.7, 380.9, 871.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [914.6, 850.7, 925.0, 871.6]}, {"text": "301.0", "bbox": [956.3, 850.7, 1003.1, 871.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1024.0, 850.7, 1034.4, 871.6]}, {"text": "314.9", "bbox": [1065.6, 850.7, 1112.5, 871.6]}, {"text": "The tax effects of the major items recorded as deferred tax assets and liabilities were as follows:", "bbox": [162.5, 915.3, 965.0, 936.2]}, {"text": "December 31", "bbox": [955.3, 960.9, 1071.7, 981.8]}, {"text": "In millions", "bbox": [162.5, 990.1,